  "preferred_name": "Electronic overload relay",
  "preferred_name_ml": {
    "en": "Electronic overload relay",
    "fr": "Relais électronique de surcharge",
    "de": "elektronisches Überlastrelais",
    "zh": "电子式过载继电器"
  },
  "definition": "inverse time-delay overload relay depending for its operation (including its time-delay) on the electronic thermal model of the current flowing in the relay",
  "definition_ml": {
    "en": "inverse time-delay overload relay depending for its operation (including its time-delay) on the electronic thermal model of the current flowing in the relay",
    "fr": "relais de surcharge à temps inverse dont le fonctionnement (y compris la temporisation) dépend du modèle thermique électronique du courant qui traverse le relais",
    "de": "abhängig verzögertes Überlastrelais oder- auslöser, dessen Betätigung (einschließlich seiner Verzögerung) von dem elektronischen Wärmemodell des im Relais fließenden Stroms abhängt",
    "zh": "反时限过载继电器的运行（包括其延时）取决于电流流过继电器时的电子热模式。"
  },
